title: [Yegharren Plain, Wooded Slope]
description: Sparkling faintly with occasional glints of moonlight, a small woodland stream runs alongside the gently sloping trail from east to west.  A fat raccoon crouches on the other side of the stream, eyeing you cautiously as he washes a piece of food in the clear water.
